sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Web as OpenKey Web
    participant API as OpenKey API
    participant TEE
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant App as Third-Party App

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over User,DB: Registration Flow
        User->>Web: Sign up (email or Google)
        Web->>API: Verify email OTP / Google token
        activate API
        API-->>Web: Account created
        deactivate API
        Web-->>User: Require passkey creation

        User->>Web: Create passkey (WebAuthn)
        Web->>API: Register passkey credential
        activate API
        API->>TEE: Generate primary key (Key 0)
        activate TEE
        TEE->>TEE: deriveKey() → seal private key
        TEE-->>API: Sealed blob
        deactivate TEE
        API->>DB: Store sealed blob
        API-->>Web: Registration complete
        deactivate API
        Web-->>User: Success
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over User,API: Login Flow
        User->>Web: Login
        Web->>API: Request passkey challenge
        activate API
        API-->>Web: Challenge
        deactivate API

        User->>Web: Passkey assertion
        Web->>API: Verify assertion
        activate API
        API-->>Web: Session token (7 days)
        deactivate API
        Web-->>User: Logged in
    end

    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note over User,App: OAuth Flow (Third-Party App)
        App->>User: Redirect to OpenKey /authorize
        User->>Web: Login + consent screen
        activate Web
        Web-->>App: Authorization code
        deactivate Web

        App->>API: Exchange code + PKCE verifier
        activate API
        API-->>App: access_token, id_token, refresh_token
        deactivate API
        Note over App: App can now access OpenKey API<br/>on behalf of user
    end
